Key Points for AI
Only generate code for the ‘Dossier Name’ field.
Use Bootstrap for layout and responsiveness.
Style in box mode (rounded corners, shadow, padding).
Make sure it’s responsive (looks good on mobile).
Use the exact label: Dossier Name (with * if required).
Do not create the whole form or component, just this field.
Refer to the provided design (image image1).
5. How to Explain to AI (Summary)
Be clear that you only want the code for one field.
Specify the tech stack (HTML, Bootstrap, CSS, TypeScript).
Mention “box mode” and “responsive” explicitly.
Reference your attached image for style and layout.
Ask for only what you need (not the whole form).
